      "name": "To-Do Item Management Card",
      "images": [],
      "summary": "A card definition for managing to-do items, encompassing fields for title, description, status (to do, in-progress, done), priority (low, medium, high), due date, and completion status. It provides multiple visual component variants—isolated, embedded, and fitted—that display to-do details with customizable layouts, styling, and labels. The components support status and priority visual cues, due date formatting, and completion indicators, facilitating flexible presentation of to-do items across different UI contexts.",
